{"tid":2440590,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"咸錫在哥登堡月薪僅為十萬克朗(九萬港紙)","createTime":"2021-03-10T05:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T07:38:22.000Z","uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ac64592d94b665605769ca1f0cc3e8700891d6a3","tid":2440590,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"據瑞迪媒體《aftonbladet》報導，咸錫在新東家哥德堡的月薪只有10萬瑞典克朗。<br />\n<br />\n咸錫與哥德堡簽下了一份8月31日到期的短期合同，他的月薪為10萬瑞典克朗。 儘管幾乎沒有花費任何代價就引進了咸錫，但在咸錫加盟後的短短幾小時內，哥德堡俱樂部就賣出了1400件有關的周邊產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UmbKTr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UmbKTr.jpg&h=eab5c3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dip1nFH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdip1nFH.jpg&h=1cd9e662&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6499369ccb976511b27403d5951f0f3c8b2177c8","tid":2440590,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b11f5c4997c8f3aaae649869918519c47152e4","tid":2440590,"uid":343520,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"少過松泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3711ebd3a0359a0ec392de3c5709b47581760379","tid":2440590,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"cctoy:好過喺支那踢波無糧出"},{"pid":"a8ba980935d31db2a1eb02649572df8d647d7177","tid":2440590,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5b11f5c4997c8f3aaae649869918519c47152e4","tid":2440590,"uid":343520,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"少過松泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\